This project is an **AI-driven decision support system** that helps farmers adopt **sustainable agriculture practices**.  
It predicts the **most suitable crop** based on soil and environmental parameters and extends towards **resource optimization** (water & fertilizer usage) to maximize yield sustainably.  

Developed on **Google Colab**, this project leverages **machine learning** to bridge the gap between raw agricultural data and actionable insights.  

